rows.label: qst700403_msg0002
rows.name:
Trying to regroup?
Smarter than I thought.

rows.label: qst700403_msg0003
rows.name: Is this the time to be impressed?

rows.label: qst700403_msg0004
rows.name:
There seems to be one leading
them. What shall we do?

rows.label: qst700403_msg0005
rows.name:
Adel, let's take out the boss. If
we defeat the one giving orders...

rows.label: qst700403_msg0006
rows.name:
It should be difficult
for them to recover.

rows.label: qst700403_msg0010
rows.name: I won't let them escape next time.

rows.label: qst700403_msg0011
rows.name:
Haha, how reliable. Looks like
I won't have any work to do.

rows.label: qst700403_msg0013
rows.name:
Well then, let's chase
after that big one.

rows.label: qst700403_msg0014
rows.name:
We should be able to get up to
the high ground from the left.
